<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.6.3">
<l>itukāṇmi ṉaṉṉaimī rikkaṭṭu viccicoṟ koṇṭunī</l>
<l>retuvāṉuñ ceytaṅkōr kaḷḷu miṟaicciyun tūvēṉmiṉ</l>
<l>matuvār tuḻāymuṭi māyap pirāṉkaḻal vāḻttiṉā</l>
<l>latuvē yivaḷuṟṟa nōykku marumarun tākumē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>See this, mothers. Taking the word of this soothsayer, don’t you,</l>
<l>doing anything, strew toddy and meat there.</l>
<l>If you praise the anklet of the marvellous lord,</l> 
	<l>[his] Tulsi crown overflowing with honey,</l>
<l>that alone will be the precious remedy for all the pain she had.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
